,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ff18fcca1143fc531f0545d83bb024152d4c7c","tid":2435083,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ea540047740d6327771d13ef0f67aad356122f","tid":2435083,"uid":171506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"航母泊日本？<br />\n<br />\n五眼應該加埋日本，台灣，印度<br />\n<br />\n可惜南韓廢柴總理奶共，應該唔會join"},{"pid":"18f9de1a7f46e7f2b248635abc6247350280175a","tid":2435083,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5953d9ed4386a0a695716658948b37b57ce66085","tid":2435083,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5109d1891112de3e6a9843e87db38d8236493830","tid":2435083,"uid":185094,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"成個2019－2020劇情真係峰回路轉，英美越行越近，歐盟同英國越行越遠，歐盟同普世價值越行越遠，英國本來奶共又越嚟越反共，本來以為出賣自己嘅原來係真朋友，真係唔識睇了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"五眼 vs 歐盟+中+俄，其他國家開始歸邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"印度 日本 台灣 係五眼"},{"pid":"3f9e7082c0142b2a983ca5e78347f204b136d20f","tid":2435083,"uid":72186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"香港人準備好效力"},{"pid":"6089a00abf0f5ff59536eeebe3f714cb19dbf068","tid":2435083,"uid":212796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f904bc483a5a27811869495bc7c0f97c85e81a9e","tid":2435083,"uid":276548,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"搵定一個軍港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前D咁靚既港口自己放棄晒 (新加坡 香港)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"5月13係英軍救星馬華人。<br />\n獨立係馬來西亞自己揀，之後先新加坡被獨立。"},{"pid":"2616ae3d217dc3282f526759a7d23ba313070595","tid":2435083,"uid":3112